# Summary
This documentation page describes the integration between Userguiding (a no-code user onboarding platform) and Amplitude, detailing the simple setup process that requires copying an Amplitude API key into the Userguiding dashboard's Integrations page to connect a single Userguiding environment to a single Amplitude project.

